~Story~

     *The waves were crashing into eachother rawring like a pack of Lions. The boat was being thrashed back and forth uncontrablly. It was too dark to see anything in the distant. The only thing you could possibly see was the water infront of you which was lite by the light of the moon. Thunder rawred in the sky showing gods anger towards everyone. The lighting flashed making more light to see infront of me. Still nothing. I tried to control the boat and steer it into a different direction. Nothing was working. In a little boat like mine what was I suppose to do. Nothing. So i excepted what most likely going to happen. The boat was going to either crash into rocks and break, or it was going to be filled with too much water and sink. Either way i was going to end up into the water and eventually drown. So i slowly let go of the wheel and slowly walked backwards. I stared into the starry night closing my eyes. Feeling every raindrop caress my face as i slowly sat down. I opened my eyes back up and took one more glance at the moon and stars. My one last final glance of life. So i took in what i could before a giant wave came in and crashed down into my boat. I felt the hard water being thrown into my face. Pushing me down and off of the boat into the water. I put my hand out as if to grab onto something, but nothing was there. I looked up from under the water seeing the boat come crashing down right into my body. I got thrown down farther into the ocean feeling every inch of pain from the boat and water.The only thing i remember is a bright light being shined above before i completly blacked out.*

                                                The Blue Balloon!!
          

                      One time I was walking down the city street.I was just walking until I saw a pretty Blue Balloon. Right when I saw that balloon I knew I had to have it. So I ran after it. It kept going higher and higer. So I would climb building stairs to try and get it. But I never did get the balloon it was gone before I could catch it. So I slowly climbed back down the stairs very upset that I couldnt get my balloon. So there I was just walking in the cold, cold night with my hands in the pockets of my coat. Very upset and not noticing my surroundings, when someone ran into me. Making me fall onto the ground. I sat there for a second till I saw someones hand come out and reach for mine. I slowly looked up to see a rather tall man."I'm sorry. I didnt see you there." The man said. I slowly took his hand as he helped me up."Its ok." I said staring at him. He was a very handsome man indeed. His deep ocean blue eyes and his brown hair that looked like he just got out of bed. "I'm Luke." he said shaking my hand. "Krystyn." I said shaking his hand in return."I'm really sorry about running into you,but i got to go." he said as he started to walk away. "Oh wait." He said when he turned back around and walked to me again. He then handed me a blue balloon. I took the blue balloon and smiled up at him. "I saw you chasing after it awhile ago and i got you another one." he said smiling. "Thanks." I said as i started to walk away. I came up to this little coffee house and walked in. I orderd my coffe and bagle and walked to a little chair and sat down. I picked up a book and started to read and enjoy the peace of the coffee house. A few hours passed and someone else walked in.I slowly looked up from my book to see the same man that had run into me. I followed him with my eyes as he walked to the counter. He ordered his food and when he was done he slowly turned around examining the coffee house. He noticed me sitting in my chair staring at him. He smiled a little before i quickly went back down to my book. I looked up one more time to see a smiling luke sitting next to me. "Small world eh?"he said to me. I smiled and nodded to him. "Yup." I said.We started to talk to eachother more and more. Finalyl a few more hours had passed and the store was closing. We exchaned number and went to our homes. That same night he called me and asked me out on another "Outing." Ever since then we had been talking and getting to know eachother more and more. Growing to like eachother every minute we were with eachother. Finally a year had passed and we started dating. It has been three years now of us dating and every moment of it has been great. I will never forget the first time we met. When he gave me my Blue Balloon, I knew it was love at first sight.
 
                       Lol i am uber cool!! Look at that amazing corny story haha!Its ok though im bored and tired and now going to go to bed. So have fun I love you all!! Nightnight!!
                                                       ~Krystyn~

Hello!! Yes I am updating though i dont know really what to say....Ummm yea this week had been again like everyother week...the same and boring. Nothing has changed...nothing ever does. Well there was a fight in lunch yesturday yet again. It wasnt that big of a fight, but it was nice. Yea so there is really nothing on my mind. I think alot...But sometimes...i think i think to much. Its really nice though to think and to dream. Especially dream or even write.Because you can dream of you fantasy and write of what you want and about your feelings. I guess it is a way of expressing for me. Im not talking about poety either...i suck at that. So that answers Michelle's question from awhile back.

 It was about how i...expressed my feelings or how i let them out. Something in that direction. I also love reading stories too. Because that as well brings you into your own fantasy world of what the writer is writing. It just maked me happy...because its a way to get away from the world. Which people need to do sometimes, or very often. I come to a conclusion of how i shouldnt really care anymore.Just go into my own fantasy, hide behind a book or something. Because that is where i really want to be. Not around people...they just bring you down more. No matter what, even the happiest person isnt happy. You see right through everyone...no one can hide anything. People should examine people more often.

There are very few happy people in there world. Some of the sad people or upset and angry people..it might just be a little thing that is bugging them and nothing really big. But it doesnt matter, if they are upset or sad then they are. And people shouldnt compare it to worst things. Because no matter what something extremly bad has happend to someone. Im not saying now when i say i want to just hide behing a book or something and not be around people..it doesnt all of a sudden mean that i want everyone to stay away from me now.But really i dont know how else to express myself in ways with out actually fully comming out. Which is something i dont want to do. So dont even bother asking seriously. I shut people out anyways. Yes it is a bad thing,but it is the best thing for me. I've realized that. When it comes to problems with me or if i am upset I dont tell people. I hide it...and when they ask its nothing. Its because i dont want people to know or to talk about it. I hate talking about my feelings...feelings suck.

They ruin everything unless you are happy. Personalities suck as well. No matter how hard you try to someone or everyone you are never the person they want you to be. Even though you should never be someone your not just for someone else. Then how else are you excepted. Your not. Thats why no one is who they really are...unless i guess you are with your friends,but even then your not. Its just not physically possible. Thats why some people are always they center of attention. Becuase they need it in order to go through life. If they dont get the attention they want then they dont know what to do with themselves. Thats why also other people dont like the attention either so they are the loner ones. But i think with the loners...is that they have tried to be the center of attention but it just didnt work for them. They have tried to get that attention.but it just didnt work. Either people just didnt listen or didnt care. So they gave up and now are seen as depressing loners when no one really understands at all. Also everyone has that someone. I mean as a friend not love.

That one friend that they really get along with. The one that they usually always hanfg out with. Even if they dont notice it or try not to exclude other people.( I am not saying this directly to anyone so shut up.) Then there is the wonderers. The one who move from friend to friend because they dont have that one. There one is someone who are just with at that moment and when they find someone else...they just go to them. So they are confused and just dont know who so they are use to so many people and sometimes forget about the later friends and people they knew. Then there are just the people who are quite. The ones who dont really have one but have different ones kind of as well. But they really dont talk to them so that is why they dont have a one. They are to quite and just dont know what to say or do. No matter how close they are to that person. its almost as if they havnt known that person even if they had known them for like there whole life.

There is just times in life when you know a person really well and you click and everything is good.Then there is times where you switch to another person you click with and dont anymore with the other person. So it is true with when you make many new friend and are with many new people. And some people that just hasnt happened yet or is still waiting i dont know. We arent going to get into the "Love" situation because...there really isnt one i guess. You dream of the love you want, your all upset because you dont have it yet, but really you just have to wait and people dont want to wait. That is the love situation its dumb and people need to come to realize that. People need to com to realize alot of things , but will that happen no. Life is a mysterious to only be found out when you die. When you die is when your life and everymeaning comes to a conclusion and only then do you know what the true meaning is. So dont question it just yet. There is a meaning but we have not gone through everything to know yet. We are only in highschool and have so much more to come. Well i guess i am done now. I actually think i have ran out of things to ramble on about. So just wait till next time till i have something even better to talk about yay! The Excitment and Suspense!!
